ACCENTURE APPLIED INTELLIGENCE

You've heard of Artificial Intelligence (AI), but what about Applied Intelligence?

AI may be the talk of the town, but it's not a silver bullet. That's where Applied Intelligence comes in: It's our unique approach to combining AI with data, analytics and automation under a bold strategic vision to transform business in a very pragmatic way. AI Centre of excellence in Poland is part of a global team of more than 6,000 deep AI experts and 3,000 data scientists. We work with almost any technology partner including SAS, AWS, GCP, and Microsoft.

We build resilient data approaches, make AI vision a reality and make it scalable. Our work makes an impact and help businesses prepare for tomorrow.

What will you do:
• Work with us at the forefront of the digital transformation contributing your creativity, innovativeness, critical thinking and technical skills to help us shape the new FinCrime landscape.
• Shape new AML and KYC solutions for major global... financial institutions across below areas:
• Design and implement new ETL processes (ingestions, transformations, data pipelines) and unified data models.
• Design, build, migrate cloud solutions;
• Develop customer segmentation;
• Tune and calibrate transaction monitoring scenarios;
• Develop new ways of detecting money laundering using Machine Learning models;
• · Implement continuous KYC processes;
• · Use analytics to draw insights and improve efficiency;
• Work in interdisciplinary teams that gather technical, business, cloud and data science competencies that deliver work in agile methodologies (at client location, remotely or mixed).
• Range of your accountability, responsibility and autonomy will depend on your experience and seniority - we are looking for specialists of varied experience levels
